ns, ensuring you develop competencies before advancing.\n\nHaptic Feedback: Feel like you're performing real tasks with tactile feedback from the controllers.\n\nInstructor Monitoring: Instructors can track your progress and practice frequency, ensuring a smooth transition from virtual to real-world competency.\n\nAccessibility: Break down traditional barriers to training, providing more opportunities for underrepresented demographics.\n\nAdult Learning Principles: The program aligns with the principles of adult learning for effective skill development.", "short_description": "BTI VR Training is a cutting-edge training tool for the biotechnical sector, ideal for those entering the biotech industry. It combines practical lab simulations with interactive theoretical lessons, providing a comprehensive learning experience. This application is a key resource for acquiring essential lab skills, serving as a bridge to the dynamic biotech world."}]}, "developer_name": "Capitol Interactive LLC", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.virtualapprentice.net/privacy-policy/new-portfolio-item-jjw66", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Virtual Apprentice LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://btiworks.org/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "514087707868786"}, {"id": "1043107547362485"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8910066185673239"}}]}, "sch